  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to provide information on the frequency of hypodontia in children cancer
      survivors receiving chemotherapy before 4 years of age.Patients who met the eligibility
      criteria will be given a structured questionnaire to fill followed by a radiographic
      examination (dental panorama) for confirmation and standardization of the results.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
